    <p>3-5 items. Each item: <strong>specific action</strong> + <strong>evidence anchor</strong> + <strong>label as adaptation / mitigation / both</strong>. Format: bulleted list. Example of a strong recommendation: "Install monitoring stations at 12 high-vulnerability coastal points along the Cooum estuary; cost ~₹40 lakh; data goes to GCC adaptation desk monthly." Example of a weak one: "Raise awareness about climate change." Don't submit the second kind. This is <strong>a T/T component and it locks today</strong> — the band becomes part of your overall T/T mark.</p>
